item.title: CVE-2023-50893|2023-12-29T11:12:36.317Z -- upsolution -- impreza%20%E2%80%93%20wordpress%20website%20and%20woocommerce%20builder
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Input During Web Page Generation ('Cross-site Scripting') vulnerability in UpSolution Impreza – WordPress Website and WooCommerce Builder allows Reflected XSS.This issue affects Impreza – WordPress Website and WooCommerce Builder: from n/a through 8.17.4.
